Mac: brew install glib

===========================================================================

Unpack into /scratch/mernst/glibc-2.3.5

rm -rf /scratch/mernst/glibc-2.3.5-build
mkdir /scratch/mernst/glibc-2.3.5-build
cd /scratch/mernst/glibc-2.3.5-build
export 'CFLAGS=-g -O0'
# This didn't work; it didn't find the linuxthreads add-on.  I'm not sure
# what is wrong.
../glibc-2.3.5/configure --enable-add-ons --prefix /scratch/mernst/glibc-2.3.5-install
